drawnet.lib.filters
Class FilterDataGSPN

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.filters.FilterData
      drawnet.lib.filters.FilterDataGSPN

public class FilterDataGSPN
extends FilterData

A class to store GSPN filter's data. It is useful to share data with other filters or solvers.

See Also:
FilterData, GSPNFilter, GSPNStaFilter

public int getDefPos(java.lang.String name)
Gets a definition position in file .def. A definition can be:
  • a color class
  • a static subclass
  • an arc function
  • a mark function

Parameters:
name - the name of the definition.
Returns:
